<slide title="PEAR::SOAP">
<list title="The good parts">
<bullet>SOAP 1.1</bullet>
<bullet>Interoperability testing done with all major implementations</bullet>
<bullet>Script based Client and Server</bullet>
<bullet>RPC/Encoded and Document/Literal</bullet>
<bullet>HTTP, HTTPS, TCP and SMTP</bullet>
<bullet>Email Server and Gateway</bullet>
<bullet>Supports 1999/2001 Schema</bullet>
<bullet>WSDL Support</bullet>
<bullet>WSDL and DISCO Generation</bullet>
<bullet>SOAP with Attachments (Mime)</bullet>
<bullet>DIME Support</bullet>
</list>
